<HTML><HEAD> <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/style.css"><Title>Jacques Maritain Center: GC 4.58a</title></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEEEEE"><A HREF="gc.htm"> Of God and His Creatures</a><hr>

<p>Hence the saying of theologians, that the end
and purpose of matrimony is <i>generare regenerandos</i>, to
generate subjects for regeneration.</p>

<hr>

